{"tid":1258251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[外國勢力] 紐約時報求訪612中信警暴傷者","createTime":"2019-06-26T04:20:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T10:12:14.000Z","uid":24805,"like":175,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"c185e11f3d1d449d7fea6bcc88780c0d173531d0","tid":1258251,"uid":24805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T04:20:27.000Z","msg":"先戴頭盔，又係我。<br />\n<br />\n受託於《紐約時報》朋友🇺🇸，依家我地需要搵<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">- 6/12中信大廈附近被圍困或被襲者<br />\n包括但不限於中催淚彈，警棍，及其他武器<br />\n<br />\n- 6/12 受襲的急救隊員</span></span><br />\n受過警察，唔係，狗隻，噬咬的巴絲打接受訪問。<br />\n今次將會有機會拍片做故，陳情傷勢<br />\n<br />\n一如既往，無人保證出足咁多位訪問，版面有幾大。<br />\n可以做既係，數Case有幾多人受傷被打、嚴重情況、<br />\n武力程度、心入面條蟲有幾多野想講出來，從而製造國際級壓力。<br />\n<br />\n身分絕對保密過八達通，安全過坐104R。<br />\n你會直接聯絡到記者及其助手<br />\n我唔會有留底，只係幫手出Post。<br />\n<br />\n肯出聲的，請 tg<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/echeung_nyt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fecheung_nyt&d=BBPgAQHQe62%2Fb%2Fw120tVmQNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=13132657\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/echeung_nyt</a>"},{"pid":"8a4fe927b8d281278bc7799db2abee360800cdec","tid":1258251,"uid":73826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T04:20:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9efdd600329728bcc714598f108ec789c853499","tid":1258251,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T04:21:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1bdf04f7ca87a6d6d26185960398ed86295e6cf7","tid":1258251,"uid":19660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T04:21:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"20c8bf844f8e4109836d2c465a7d98f2cbe7f4e7","tid":1258251,"uid":15477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T04:25:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d10aef73aee86af588cd231330873cba9e3bcd80","tid":1258251,"uid":162073,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T04:26:56.000Z","msg":"斯諾登都唔驚我地點會驚"},{"pid":"6e70bc53dd56a1a8ee325828ce06a837ae4bf65e",